About Me
I am a simple and easy going man,I do not like the night life,I like taking a walk by the beach and watching the sunset,I enjoy cooking,I need a woman who is honest and faithful,one who would love me as much as I do her,and one who enjoy some of the things that I enjoy also.am looking forward hearing from you soon.Thank you and God bless you.Thanks……. Johnny
